answers.question: What is training-serving skew and how do you prevent it?
answers.answer_text: So, training service serving SKU is the disperency between the data logic used to train an ML model and the data logic it encounters during the production interference. This misarrangment leads to poor and unexpected model performance in real-world scenarios. There can be multiple causes as well which can be feature engineering differences or data drifting. So, for preventing it there are multiple ways. First is unified pipelines feature stores or you can use monitoring and alert system for that.
